@node BLACK "Black Lotus"

@{b}Black Lotus@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = A/B/UL(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 0
Artist  = Christopher Rush

Text(UL): <T>: Adds 3 mana of any single color of your choice to your mana
          pool, then is discarded. Tapping this artifact can be played as
          an interrupt.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_B.guide/LOTUS}

@endnode
@node CHAOS "Chaos Orb"

@{b}Chaos Orb@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = A/B/UL(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 2
Artist  = Mark Tedin

Text(UL): <1T>: Flip Chaos Orb onto the playing area from a height of at
          least one foot. Chaos Orb must turn completely over at least
          once or it is discarded with no effect. When Chaos Orb lands,
          any cards in play that it touches are destroyed, as is Chaos Orb.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_C.guide/C_ORB}

@endnode
@node COPPE "Copper Tablet"

@{b}Copper Tablet@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = A/B/UL(U)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 2
Artist  = Amy Weber

Text(UL): Copper Tablet does 1 damage to each player during his or her
          upkeep.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_C.guide/COPPE}

@endnode
@node CYCLO "Cyclopean Tomb"

@{b}Cyclopean Tomb@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = A/B/UL(R)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 4
Artist  = Anson Maddocks

NOTE: Casting cost is missing on the Alpha version !!

Text(UL): <2T>: Turn any one non-swamp land into swamp during upkeep.
          Mark the changed lands with tokens. If Cyclopean Tomb is
          destroyed, remove one token of your choice each upkeep,
          returning that land to its original nature.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_C.guide/CTOMB}

@endnode
